cs.DB, cs.LO, cs.DS, cs.AI, cs.CC 

This paper deals with parameterizations of database instances and queries, and evaluates query evaluation in fixed-parameter tractable combined complexity. This topic is closely related to databases (cs.DB), logic in computer science (cs.LO), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and computational complexity (cs.CC).
